ext_descriptions.ext_description:
The property_type defines the type of characteristic that is specified for an object. The following values shall be used:
'centroid': The 'property_value' identifies the center point of the mass of a body. The relative position of this point within the body is an invariant datum relative to rotation and translation.;
'surface area': The 'property_value' specifies the overall surface of the bodies contained in the referenced shape;
'volume': The 'property_value' specifies the overall volume of the bodies contained in the referenced shape.
